  "3179350": {
    "name": "Long Drive North: 合作房车模拟器",
    "steam_appid": 3179350,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可选择独自一人，或与最多4名玩家分别驾驶4辆房车一同冒险。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >驾驶、维护、探索、搜集、狩猎，这就是你在《Long Drive North》中的生存之道。 </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >驾驶你那辆可靠的旧房车，做好车辆维护，亲手完成加油与修理工作 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在残酷世界中求生：控制疲劳、饥渴和口渴水平，搜集零件，并通过狩猎获得食物 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >按照食谱烹饪，保证充分进食 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索荒野：进入开放世界沙盒环境，探秘灾后美洲荒野 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可选择脚踏实地丈量边疆，也可驾车从中穿越。那么，你能征服荒野，在这场绝望之旅中生存下来吗？ </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可选择独自一人，或在多人合作模式中与最多4名玩家分别驾驶房车一同冒险。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Long Drive North》的灵感发源于《The Long Dark》、《The Long Drive》以及《My Summer Car》等游戏。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179350/extras/aa508930a944ef1c1be35fd6fc89dc66.poster.avif?t=1772186527\" aria-label=\"A short, looping video showing driving an RV through a snowy environment in 1st person with smoke rising from the bonnet. The smoking engine parts under the hood are then shown.\" width=780 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179350/extras/aa508930a944ef1c1be35fd6fc89dc66.webm?t=1772186527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179350/extras/aa508930a944ef1c1be35fd6fc89dc66.mp4?t=1772186527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的房车虽然略显破旧，但仍然是辆可靠的座驾。这辆房车就是你在旅途中的庇护所，所以一定要记得精心维护。不要害怕弄脏双手，打开引擎盖，在这款汽车模拟器中亲自修理房车并为其加油。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179350/extras/10fb37b007d0e8499097467296854d95.poster.avif?t=1772186527\" aria-label=\"A clip of 1st person hunting. The player character&#039;s arm and a rifle can be seen, as the player approaches a watchtower. Then the video cuts to showing a deer and the character shoots.\" width=780 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179350/extras/10fb37b007d0e8499097467296854d95.webm?t=1772186527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179350/extras/10fb37b007d0e8499097467296854d95.mp4?t=1772186527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你，离家万里，迷失在陌生而又危险的大地之上。从废弃的汽车和破败的建筑中搜集零件。带上狩猎步枪和狗狗伙伴，踏入荒野展开狩猎——巧用食谱，烹饪食物，在旅途之中求得生存。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >控制疲劳、饥饿和口渴水平，克服严酷恶劣的环境，跨过一路上的艰难险阻。直面多变的天气状况，保持警惕，避开频发的危险风暴。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179350/extras/15e3ef37de3226cfbef05bd28f1fc00b.poster.avif?t=1772186527\" aria-label=\"A video showing multiple RVs driving along a road in a convoy in a snowy American wilderness environment. The video then cuts to show four RVs parked up on an overlook, with a campfire lit nearby.\" width=780 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179350/extras/15e3ef37de3226cfbef05bd28f1fc00b.webm?t=1772186527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179350/extras/15e3ef37de3226cfbef05bd28f1fc00b.mp4?t=1772186527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >脚踏实地丈量边疆，或者驾车从中穿越。跨越灾后美洲荒野，发现这开放世界沙盒环境中的雄奇与凶险。</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 韩语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 俄语, 简体中文, 繁体中文, 土耳其语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
